16. Key Optimizations

Three elements provide the biggest improvement:

1. RT Kernel
PREEMPT_RT
2. Network Stack
GRO/GSO/TSO disabled
EEE disabled
fq scheduler
3. CPU Isolation
isolcpus
nohz_full
rcu_nocbs
17. Rebuilding the System

Installation order:

1 install Debian
2 install RT kernel
3 configure kernel boot parameters
4 configure sysctl tuning
5 configure NIC tuning
6 install Audirvana
7 configure systemd service
8 configure storage (/mnt/music)
9 configure Diretta renderer
